🔥 🔄 FULL FLOW (ONE LINE)

👉
User → Page → SSR → API → Data → UI → Click → SSR → API → UI → Action → API → Update → SSR → UI

🧠 SUPER SIMPLE VERSION

👉

Page open → server data laata hai
Click → new page → server data laata hai
Add → backend save karta hai
Redirect → updated data dikhata hai
